{"tid":2361103,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"打邊爐阻止朋友眼闊肚窄被屌度縮孤寒","createTime":"2021-01-10T11:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T11:53:52.000Z","uid":133727,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f1db3beb5f3dbc0b89023aa4999b0841587cfdb8","tid":2361103,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:13:17.000Z","msg":"次次都買勁多食唔哂<br />\n一係咁飽到嘔夾硬食<br />\n一係就倒哂佢<br />\n<br />\n第二次打邊爐買料時不斷叫佢買少啲<br />\n比佢屌番轉頭話間唔中先打一次咪咁煩<br />\n唔好咁度縮<br />\n<br />\n但明知食唔哂又係倒<br />\n點解唔買少啲<br />\n<br />\n比佢屌完諗自己係咪真係咁度縮唔識享受<br />\n佢咁樣算唔算情緒勒索<br />\n同埋可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844acb4d475587b398d93052951d654754bebb8c","tid":2361103,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c92cdd5b43a4e3ae46582897d4f9938130e6c11","tid":2361103,"uid":85586,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"食剩嘅拎返屋企煮咪得<br />\n點解要倒"},{"pid":"792351e5e10729a18cc8f11ac0ce6fd6a8e0be9b","tid":2361103,"uid":50088,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c92cdd5b43a4e3ae46582897d4f9938130e6c11","tid":2361103,"uid":85586,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"食剩嘅拎返屋企煮咪得<br />\n點解要倒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n尤其而家咁凍<br />\n唔驚變壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddada272ac317bbf6db464746b39af547925489","tid":2361103,"uid":154255,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T11:17:51.000Z","msg":"食唔哂咪唔落囉on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cca17e9a2c5cd65ce9de97f2ce0637a65dca38","tid":2361103,"uid":126642,"like":0,"dislike":0,